\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Calculate total length of items on selected tracks\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Sums up the lengths of all items and breaks the result down by track and media source file. If you use markers named {\f1 =START} and/or {\f1 =END}, anything outside that range is disregarded.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Instructions\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab select one or more tracks\par}
